::Battera::

She looks at him in terror as he pins her to the wall and has his 
claws to her neck.  She puts her hands on his arms to try to pull his 
claws away from her neck.  She starts to feel a tear run down her 
cheek. "Please, I"m here for a peace conference. Please, let me go. 
Please." She pleads and looks at him with fear in her eyes.
